00:00:02.700 --> 00:00:04.260
Part 6. Trolling motor testings continue.

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:10.380
Problem started to unravel. Simply the batteries were over from remote controller.

00:00:11.680 --> 00:00:15.020
So lets open it up and see what we can find from inside.

00:00:17.260 --> 00:00:19.460
From inside we can find different kind of components.

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:23.660
