So we just get the old battery off and put a new one instead.

00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:40.240
Battery has a number code which makes it easy to find a correct one from a shop.

00:00:40.314 --> 00:00:43.734
Most likely they cost only few euros. So you will not end up empty pocket.

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:48.900
Now just put new battery in and cover back so we can go back testing.

00:00:48.900 --> 00:00:50.054
How it will go?

00:00:50.460 --> 00:00:53.720
We got power on the motor and our spirit is high.

